text.section:
An application to register under subsection (a) of this section shall include:
The applicant's name and address;
The make, model, license number, and vehicle identification number of any vehicle that the applicant will use to transport waste kitchen grease;
A description of the operations to be performed by the applicant; and
Proof of vehicle insurance with personal injury and property damage combined single limit liability limits of at least $1,000,000.
